<hymn_number>6204</hymn_number>
<title>dạymaⁿạ bạsạ̉l</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dạymaⁿạ bạsạ̉l nfsy lyh yswʿ jh ʿlsẖạny
 wsạb ạlmlạykẗ wjh llạrḍ fqyr
 ạtʿạqb bdạly wsẖạly ʿny ạ̉ḥmạly
 wbdạlhạ ạdạly ḥb wqlb wkbyr lyh
 lạ̉n ạllh mḥbẗ ạllh mḥbẗ
 lyh yswʿ bysạmḥ lmạ bạgẖlṭ fy ḥqh
 lmạ ạ̉jylh btwbẗ wạ̉nạ qlby ndmạn
 bynsy̱ ạlkẖṭyẗ wymsḥ dmʿ ʿyny
 wymsk ạ̹ydy wykẖlyny frḥạn</lyrics>
</song>